@page "/"

<PageTitle>Recipe Meal Planner</PageTitle>

<h1>Recipe & Meal Planning Application</h1>

<p>
    Welcome to the Recipe & Meal Planning Application. This app helps users
    manage recipes, create meal plans, and organize grocery lists.
</p>

<h3>Features</h3>

<ul>
    <li>Create, edit, and delete recipes</li>
    <li>Plan meals for specific dates</li>
    <li>Create and manage grocery lists</li>
    <li>Organize meal preparation in one place</li>
</ul>

<p>
    Use the navigation menu to access Recipes, Meal Planner, Grocery List,
    and Help.
</p>